public class HvdcLine2TImpl
extends BranchImpl
implements HvdcLine2T

An implementation of the model object 'Line2 T'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Compond R
  • Control Mode
  • Meter End
  • Control Side
  • Power Demand
  • Scheduled DC Voltage
  • Rectifier
  • Inverter
